    dc:creator "Favorito, Sandra E.; Zanata, Angela M.; Assumpção, Maria I." ;
    dc:date "2005" ;
    dc:title "A new Synbranchus (Teleostei: Synbranchiformes: Synbranchidae) from ilha de Marajó, Pará, Brazil, with notes on its reproductive biology and larval development" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566930>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566932>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566934>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566936>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566938>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566940> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566930>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Synbranchus lampreia, holotype, MZUSP 50184, 986.0 mm TL; Brazil, Pará, ilha de Marajó, rio Goiapi. General view on top, lateral view of anterior portion of body on center, and ventral view at bottom." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4566930/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566932>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Color pattern of (a) Synbranchus lampreia, MPEG 3377, 704.0 mm TL, and (b) Synbranchus marmoratus, MPEG 3375, 630.0 mm TL. Both from Brazil, Pará, ilha de Marajó, rio Goiapi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4566932/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566934>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Map of part of northern Brazil showing the type locality of Synbranchus lampreia. Brazil, Pará, ilha de Marajó, rio Goiapi, tributary ofrioArari, Cachoeira doArari,approx.0°58’S 48°57’W." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4566934/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566936>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Type locality of Synbranchus lampreia. (a) rio Goiapi and collecting site, and (b) burrow containing nest." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4566936/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566938>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Eggs and larval stages of Synbranchus lampreia. (a) egg in Stage A; (b) larva in Stage C; (c) larva in Stage D, general view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4566938/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4566940>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Eggs and larval stages of Synbranchus lampreia. (a) anterior portion of larva in Stage D; (b) larva in Stage E, and (c) anterior portion of juvenile in Stage F." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4566940/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

